WEBVTT

00:01:56.800 --> 00:02:00.360
Elizabeth has pseudoxanthoma elasticum,

00:02:01.440 --> 00:02:03.000
PXE for short.

00:02:04.880 --> 00:02:07.176
Questions mix with fear

00:02:07.200 --> 00:02:09.400
and erupt like bile in my throat.

00:02:09.919 --> 00:02:11.640
Why are you looking in her eyes?

00:02:12.840 --> 00:02:15.816
What do you know about this?
How do you know for sure?

00:02:15.840 --> 00:02:17.320
What is the prognosis?

00:02:18.200 --> 00:02:21.920
My training in pastoral counseling
did not prepare me for this.

00:02:23.680 --> 00:02:27.560
Dr. Bercovitch tells us
everything he knows about PXE.

00:02:28.840 --> 00:02:30.600
It's a rare genetic disorder,